data.description: Bring your animals and enjoy country living in this gorgeous custom built Richardson home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 3 car garage, office or bonus room, large laundry/mud room with a half bath toilet/sink. New roof and gutters on the home were completed 12/1/2023. This property features two parcels being sold together (3.58 acres total). The home is within the inactive HOA of the Humphrey Estates. Here you will find that the property features an outdoor underground storm shelter, a double RV carport and huge shop with cement floors, electric, and two roll up doors for all of your projects. The separate mini garage is perfect for storing lawn equipment or for additional parking with its roll up garage door. The additional parcel features pipe fencing and is unrestricted for raising livestock and there are no building restrictions in Grady County. Utilities include OEC electric, Fiberoptic internet w/Pioneer or OEC, water well, septic, trash w/OK Waste Co, (rented) Morrison Propane tank that provides gas for the 50 gal hot water tank & heat furnace. Inactive HOA dues is $50/yr road maintenance completed in spring/fall. Seller accepted a Contingency contract with a 24 hr kick out clause.
